maude-3555358">“开局并不顺利”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/halle-berry-remembers-important-role-the-flintstones-big-step-forward-black-women-3760022">哈莉·贝瑞 (Halle Berry) 回忆起《摩登原始人》中的“重要”角色，认为黑人女性“向前迈出了一大步”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
格拉斯顿伯里宣布计划庆祝已故的安妮·南丁格尔https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-announces-plans-to-celebrate-the-late-annie-nightingale-3759988?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=glastonbury-announces-plans-to-celebrate-已故的安妮·南丁格尔Tom SkinnerTue, 28 May 2024 09:58:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3759988 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安妮·南丁格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>致敬活动将在 The Glade 和 BBC Introducing Stage 举行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-announces-plans-to-celebrate-the-late-annie-nightingale-3759988">格拉斯顿伯里宣布庆祝已故安妮·南丁格尔计划的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安妮·南丁格尔" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/AnnieNightingale-Glastonbury-Festival-tributes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>宣布计划在今年的音乐节上庆祝已故<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/annie-nightingale">安妮·南丁格尔</a>的一生。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/broadcasting-legend-annie-nightingale-dies-aged-83-3569896">这位传奇 DJ 和广播员于 1 月 11 日在短暂患病后去世</a>。她已经83岁了。在当时的致敬活动中，Glasto 联合组织者 Emily Eavis 将南丁格尔描述为“一位女性开拓者和真正的狂热者”。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024：查看迄今为止的完整阵容和舞台划分</a></strong></li></ul><p>她继续说道：“安妮在我20多岁的时候给了我很多支持，我一直很感激有这样一个坚强的女人一路上鼓励我，我相信她也为许多像我这样的人做了同样的事情。</p><p> “她激励了许多音乐、广播及其他领域的女性，她是一个可爱的人。”</p><p>今天（5 月 28 日），Glastonbury 分享了有关将于 6 月 27 日星期四在沃西农场举办的活动向南丁格尔致敬的详细信息。</p><p> “安妮·南丁格尔喜欢格拉斯顿伯里音乐节，”帖子开头说道。 “她的 BBC Radio 1 节目在整个 2000 年代的音乐节上每周四晚在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-romy-kelly-lee-owens-shygirl-and-more-added-to-glastonbury-as-silver-hayes-line-up-revealed-3751900">Silver Hayes</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-fatboy-slim-camelphat-groove-armada-lead-glastonbury-2024-glade-area-line-up-3749471">The Glade</a>播出，她上次在音乐节上表演是在 2017 年，是在 Glade 主舞台上。</p><p> “因此，安妮一生的庆祝活动于周四在林间空地开始，然后转移到 BBC 介绍舞台进行天黑后的第二部分，这是很合适的。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7gZ8OIKqXW/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 